WITH AND WITHOUT YOU. Second edition by Jacob Aue Sobol is a tribute to his father who died when he was 20 years old. Printed on Jacobs 40th birthday it is a compilation of all the projects that he has made and that his father never got to see.

If you buy one book from Jacob this should be it. It has key images from all of his work including the yet unpublished projects Home, Road Of Bones and America as well as Sabine, The Gomez Brito Family, Arrivals and Departures, By the River of Kings and I, Tokyo.

See more at www.jacobauesobol.com 

HB, 189 mm x 252 mm, 129 tritone images, 224 pages. Published by @superlabo

With And Without You is also available with a print (paper size 240x240mm) (image size 180x120mm). Museum Quality Pigment Paper

Hej derude. @saraauesobol her. Jeg er italiener men har boet i Danmark siden 2014. Jeg tog billeder af mennesker, familier og par i Mexico, USA, Rusland og omkring Europa for at lave mine egne projekter. Nu vil jeg gerne lave et projekt om sammenhold i Brøndby Strand. Jeg søger efter mennesker, der bor alene eller familier, der bor i højhusene.

Mit mål er at portrættere fællesskabet og det multikulturelle samfund i Brøndby Strand. Jeg vil gerne give en stemme til de “almindelige” mennesker og deres hverdagsliv. 
Skriv her eller på min email saraauesobol@gmail.com hvis du kende nogen der bo der, du/I har lyst til at vide mere - eller hvis jeg kan komme hos jer og tage billeder.

Som tak for at deltage, kan jeg give jer et billede efter mit besøg.
